@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.72 * v2 + 0.32)) - 0.61)
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.77)))
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.46 + v1 + 0.73) + (tmp + 0.07 / v0 + 0.88)) + v0)
    v1 = 0.23
    data[tid] = v0
